            <div class="work-card__overlay">
              <a href="https://jdoedden.gensparkspace.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="work-card__link">アプリを体験する →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="work-card__body">
            <span class="work-card__type">WEBアプリ</span>
            <h3 class="work-card__title">経営診断WEBアプリ</h3>
            <p class="work-card__desc">5問のQ&Aで経営の課題を即診断。AIが回答を分析し、最適なアクションを提案するインタラクティブなアプリ。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="work-card fade-in">
          <div class="work-card__img work-card__img--dark">
            <img src="images/eigyo-tool.png" alt="営業自動化ツール">
          </div>
          <div class="work-card__body">
            <span class="work-card__type">自動化ツール</span>
